ustration on its unforgiving Nightmare difficulty. <br><br></li><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">One More from Falcom Sound Team jdk</h2>Nihon Falcom is known for its brilliant music, and the <i>Trails</i> series has never been an exception, with <i>the 3rd</i> adding dozens of new tracks to keep players engaged as they journey through Phantasma.<br><br></li><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Even More Olivier</h2>As if two Sky games was enough Olivier.</li></ul>",
